text: call.center is a softphone for OS X, Windows, Android and iOS. It uses Session Initiation Protocol for communication. call.center is distributed as free software. call.center is a standalone softphone and not a VoIP service. A VoIP service or subscription is required to make or receive calls. == Audio codecs == * OPUS * G.711 family codec (PCMA, PCMU); * GSM; == External links == * call.center website Category:VoIP software
